_sText:
De_frames
Place in cs source map directory.

Entire map is made of either white or black brushes (except water & sky), to give a wireframe feel to it. There are two bombsites, one at ct spawn.  20 spawn points for each team.  This map trys to focus on tactics & gameplay rather than visuals (though the visuals arn't bad - just not realistic).  Most of the map favors close in weapons, though there are a few areas where snipers will have a definate advantage.  

Size: 7102KB
Type: Demolition
Spawns: 20 each for t's and ct's - 40 Total (Not recommended tho)
Author: MaelstroMGooF
Feedback: samgilligan@gmail.com
